dc_description_s: This data layer displays information about public recreation and conservation lands in Washtenaw County, Michigan. It was created by the Washtenaw County Parks and Recreation Commission for planning and web application use. Data is based on WC GIS parcel data, legal descriptions in the WCPARC files, review of Park and Recreation Plans prepared by various LUG's, and data received from HCMA, MDNR, and various land preservation and conservation organizations.
